{"tid":1149240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范國威會議室內跌倒　由擔架抬走送院","createTime":"2019-05-11T04:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T04:57:41.000Z","uid":113626,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c0e4da13566f7c058d91c0282221917d731b19","tid":1149240,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"由民主黨涂謹申及經民聯石禮謙主持的立法會修訂《逃犯條例》法案委員會，分別在早上8時半和9時開會，地點同樣在會議室1。石禮謙及其他建制派議員進入會議室1時，場面一度混亂，兩派議員互相指罵和推撞，有人跌倒。當建制派議員進入會議室1之後，兩派議員對峙，有議員互相拉扯、對罵，亦有議員站上檯面，僵持15分鐘後建制派離開會議室1。<br />\n<br />\n期間新民主同盟的范國威在會議室內跌倒，他在公民黨議員郭家麒的陪同下，由救護員用擔架床抬走及送院，范國威離開會議室時要用氧氣罩協助呼吸。<br />\n<br />\n民主派選出的法案委員會主席、民主黨涂謹申表示，會議仍然由他主持，任何其他議員聲稱選舉主持都是不合法。"},{"pid":"94b254c23dece055596fc3da83986baf0de511d0","tid":1149240,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:26:26.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"87c3c5fd26790fe67d3e92a29f7639fd638b7975","tid":1149240,"uid":94739,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"唔講以為佢中槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd2e20161993a54bb6fedf7585aa48b8a3cb716","tid":1149240,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:28:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8b5a819c6189381901c3d496c3b184aa59392e2","tid":1149240,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87c3c5fd26790fe67d3e92a29f7639fd638b7975","tid":1149240,"uid":94739,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"唔講以為佢中槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abd9b8f86cd61bc33f5ba7e41ebef22a341973a","tid":1149240,"uid":52090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:36:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190511/59588553\" dat